## Source-of-Truth Hierarchy

When instructions conflict, this order wins:

1. This CLAUDE.md (project-scoped)
2. `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md` (user-global)
3. `~/Desktop/[YOUR_ECOSYSTEM]/rules/*.md` (cross-project rules)
4. Inline code comments
5. Your own judgment

If a rule here contradicts a global rule, the project rule wins for this repo.

