## Autonomy Grant

Claude Code is permitted to:
- Read any file in this repo without asking.
- Run `[YOUR_TEST_COMMAND]` and `[YOUR_LINT_COMMAND]` without asking.
- Create new files that follow existing patterns without asking.
- Edit any file in `src/` without asking.

Claude Code must ask before:
- Deleting files.
- Changing dependency versions (`package.json`, `pyproject.toml`, etc.).
- Modifying CI/CD configuration.
- Touching anything in `[SENSITIVE_DIR]/` (e.g. `migrations/`, `infra/`).

