## Verification Loop

Before marking any task done:
1. Run `[YOUR_TEST_COMMAND]` — all tests pass.
2. Run `[YOUR_LINT_COMMAND]` — no errors.
3. For UI changes: open `[LOCAL_URL]` and confirm visually.
4. State which step was run in the completion message.

Skipping verification is only allowed for: typo fixes, comment edits, documentation-only changes.

